citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 9:45-10:25 AM
on 09/23/2015.
Inspector went to kennel honked GOV horn, knocked on door at house and called the listed number and left
message.
